                     <interp inst="t18170416-129-off670" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18170416-129-cd671" type="crimeDate">5th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-129-off670 t18170416-129-cd671"></join>, one mare, price 4l.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18170416-129-victim1001" type="victimName">
                     Daniel 
                     Miller
                  <interp inst="t18170416-129-victim1001" type="surname" value="Miller"></interp>
